<reggrp_short_dscr>:
SD Power configuration
------------------------------
<reggrp_public_text>:
Contains set of two power configurations which are applied to the SD lane in normal mode or in quiet mode.
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
Power settings for NORMAL mode.
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
Power Down Control settings for SD Lane in NORMAL mode

Bits 17 to 19 are for TX direction, other bits are for RX direction.
The default value is power-down mode, to ensure low power usage after reset. Needs to be configured to a power-up mode as part of serdes configuration.
------------------------------
<field_enc>:
Refer to GUC documentation
------------------------------
